description.content:
CONTACT ME FOR CUSTOM GIGS AND PRICING


Hi, I'm James, a design and development expert. I create professional, conversion-focused websites that make your business stand out. I've helped 75+ satisfied clients build their perfect website.


What sets my service apart:


  • Design-First Approach: All designs are created in Figma for your approval before Webflow development begins. This approach lets you see concepts faster and make adjustments early.
  • Pixel Perfect Responsive: Beautiful on every device, from phones to desktops.
  • SEO & Hosting: Full search engine optimization to boost your search rankings, plus domain and hosting setup.
  • Clear & Prompt Communication: You can expect constant communication about the status of your site.
  • Video Consultations: Have more questions or just want to chat face to face? We can schedule video calls to go over the site together.
  • Post Launch Support: Unlimited revisions to ensure you get your perfect website. And free post launch support for questions and adjustments.


Do you have more advanced requirements? Reach out to me so we can discuss your business needs and build a tailored solution for you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you Webflow Certified?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I have my Webflow Partner Certification. I have taken and passed all of the exams offered through the Webflow partner program.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you have a portfolio?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I have a large collection of portfolio projects I can share with you. Start a conversation with me so I can send you the list of projects.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long will it take for my website to be complete?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Every website has different requirements, but I find most standard business websites take 3-4 weeks for everything to be completed and launched.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Does the website include SEO?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Every website is made to rank highly in google search results. All of the HTML code, content, and SEO tags will be optimized for results.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you integrate third-party apps into my site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can help you integrate any third-party app to your site such as Zapier, Airtable, MemberStack, and many more. I can also connect your site to any API using my backend server or cloud functions.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you create a website from my existing Figma/Sketch/XD design.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can definitely create a website based on your existing design.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you work with templates?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I build every project from scratch, but if you have a template you really like then I can build you a website that closely matches the provided template.
